Package server.proxy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IProxy
    This interface defines the actions that can be taken with the server.
    IProxyDevCardCommands
    Contains all of the commands that are called on the server relating to playing cards.

    This interface is extended by IProxyMoveAPI.
    IProxyGameCommands
    This contains all of the queries and actions that can be taken with the game before joining the game.

    This interface is extended by IProxyNonMoveAPI.
    IProxyMoveAPI
    Contains the commands/actions that you can take for a game that your are currently in.
    IProxyNonMoveAPI
    All operations that have to do with users as well as server utility methods are contained in this interface.

    This interface is used by IProxy.
    IProxyPlayingCommands
